title: Maldives GDP From Construction
description: GDP from Construction in Maldives decreased to 3267.70 MVR Million in 2021 from 3437.50 MVR Million in 2020. GDP from Construction in Maldives averaged 2211.99 MVR Million from 1995 until 2021, reaching an all time high of 5133.80 MVR Million in 2019 and a record low of 441 MVR Million in 1996. This page provides - Maldives Gdp From Construction- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Maldives Monetary Authority
